original: Yllner, Nils Gustaf Natanael, tandläkare, Norrköping, f. 16/8/95 i Höja, Kristianst. 1., av kontr :prosten Axel Y. o. Ida Trägårdh. G. 21 m. Tyra Lind. Barn: Rolf f. 22, odont. kand., Ingegerd 26, Birgitta 32. — Stud:ex. v. Östra real i Sthlm 15, ing:ex. i Stre-litz 20, tandhkand. 25, tandläk. 27. Praktik i Norrköp. sed. 27. Ordf. i Odont. fören. 26-27.
translated:
Yllner, Nils Gustaf Natanael, dentist, Norrköping, b. 16/8/95 in Höja, Kristianstad County, 1st Parish, of the clergyman Axel Y. and Ida Trägårdh. Married in 1921 to Tyra Lind. Children: Rolf, b. 1922, dental student, Ingegerd, b. 1926, Birgitta, b. 1932. 

Education: Graduated from Östra real in Stockholm in 1915, engineering degree from Stre-litz in 1920, dental degree in 1925, licensed dentist in 1927. 

Practiced dentistry in Norrköping since 1927. Served as chairman of the Dental Association in 1926-1927.
